                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On December 23, the Italian Chamber approved the law ratifying the Paris
                    Agreements by a vote of 335 to 215, making a total of 550 deputies out of 590
                    participating in the vote. Information on the Italian vote of ratification was
                    transmitted to the Department of State <pb facs="0451" n="1519" xml:id="pg_1519"
                    /> in telegram 2336 from Rome, December 23, and despatch 1314 from Rome,
                    December 30 (765.00/12–2354 and 765.00/12–3054, respectively).</p>
            </div>
        </body>
